{
  "texts": [
    "Each session will include a warm-up exercise (5 minutes), a main exercise (40 minutes), and a cool-down exercise (5 minutes).",
    "The main activity will consist of diverse components such as aerobic training, resistance training, balance training, and mindfulness meditation training.",
    "The feedback will be given during PA courses if the participants have questions.",
    "Each PA session will be delivered by a PA coach with the assistance of two to four research helpers to ensure safety and feasibility.",
    "Each diet session will consist of two parts: health education on diet (30 minutes) and nutrition counseling (30 minutes)."
  ]
}